ogservice-1", "checkoutservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-02": [], "aiops-k8s-03": ["shippingservice-2", "recommendationservice-1", "frontend-0", "cartservice-0", "adservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-04": ["paymentservice-2", "frontend-2", "currencyservice-1", "checkoutservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-05": ["paymentservice-1", "cartservice-1", "currencyservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-06": ["productcatalogservice-0", "checkoutservice-2", "emailservice-2"], "aiops-k8s-07": ["emailservice-0", "frontend-1", "currencyservice-2", "adservice-1", "shippingservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-08": ["paymentservice-0", "redis-cart-0", "recommendationservice-0", "productcatalogservice-2", "adservice-2", "cartservice-2"]}, "matched_anomaly": "A fault was detected from 2025-06-13T17:10:04Z to 2025-06-13T17:20:04Z. Please analyze its root cause.", "time_range": "2025-06-13 17:10:04+00:00 to 2025-06-13 17:20:04+00:00"}, "metric_data_collected": true, "node_pod_mapping": {"aiops-k8s-01": ["recommendationservice-2", "shippingservice-0", "emailservice-1", "productcatalogservice-1", "checkoutservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-02": [], "aiops-k8s-03": ["shippingservice-2", "recommendationservice-1", "frontend-0", "cartservice-0", "adservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-04": ["paymentservice-2", "frontend-2", "currencyservice-1", "checkoutservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-05": ["paymentservice-1", "cartservice-1", "currencyservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-06": ["productcatalogservice-0", "checkoutservice-2", "emailservice-2"], "aiops-k8s-07": ["emailservice-0", "frontend-1", "currencyservice-2", "adservice-1", "shippingservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-08": ["paymentservice-0", "redis-cart-0", "recommendationservice-0", "productcatalogservice-2", "adservice-2", "cartservice-2"]}, "available_metric_names": ["client_error_ratio", "error_ratio", "pod_cpu_usage", "rrt", "rrt_max", "server_error_ratio"], "log_analysis_findings": "在分析UUID为37de08d4-269的故障期间，从2025-06-13T17:10:04Z到2025-06-13T17:20:04Z的系统日志中提取到以下关键信息：\n\n### 检测到的日志关键词\n- `context canceled`\n- `rpc error`\n\n### 分析结果\n\n#### 错误组件和原因假设\n1. **组件**: `frontend`\n   - **原因**: 多个日志显示`rpc error: code = Canceled desc = context canceled`，表明服务在尝试获取推荐产品和检索货币信息时遇到了中断。\n   - **证据**: 日志信息例如 \"failed to get product recommendations: rpc error: code = Canceled desc = context canceled\" 出现频次高，尤其是在访问产品推荐的情况下。\n\n### 综合分析\n这个故障主要集中在`frontend`服务上执行RPC调用时遇到的`context canceled`错误。这通常意味着请求被主动中止或者未能在预期的时间内响应，很可能与RPC调用的服务无效或不稳定有关。\n\n### 输出格式\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"context canceled\", \"rpc error\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"RPC调用因'context canceled'错误中止，可能导致请求未能完成。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"“failed to get product recommendations: rpc error: code = Canceled desc = context canceled” 频次较高\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n这种错误模式通常与后端服务响应的超时或网络波动有关，需要进一步核对网络、后端服务状态及其响应时间以排查根因。", "metric_analysis_findings": "根据分析结果，在故障期间检测到多种异常指标。以下是显著的异常调用链和相关实体：\n\n### 发现异常指标：\n- 服务性能指标：\n  - `checkoutservice` 的 `error_ratio` 和 `client_error_ratio` 显著增加。\n  - `frontend` 和 `cartservice` 多个 Pod 的 `error_ratio`, `client_error_ratio`, `server_error_ratio` 增加。\n  - `recommendationservice` 和 `productcatalogservice` 服务存在 `rrt_max` 增长。\n  - `shippingservice` 服务中多个 Pod 的 `client_error_ratio` 和 `error_ratio` 增加。\n\n### 具体异常组件及原因：\n1. **Frontend Service:**\n   - **组件**: `frontend-0`, `frontend-1`, `frontend-2`\n   - **原因**: `rrt` 和 `rrt_max` 指标异常增长。\n   - **证据**: `rrt_max` 从正常的 225266.5 增长到故障期间的 60001668.0。\n\n2. **Checkout Service:**\n   - **组件**: `checkoutservice-0`, `checkoutservice-2`\n   - **原因**: `error_ratio` 和 `client_error_ratio` 显著增加。\n   - **证据**: `error_ratio` 增幅达到 14.81 和 13.59。\n\n3. **Recommendation Service:**\n   - **组件**: `recommendationservice-2`\n   - **原因**: `rrt_max` 和 `rrt` 显著增长。\n   - **证据**: `rrt_max` 从正常的 17457.64 增长到 328421565.46。\n\n4. **Shipping Service:**\n   - **组件**: `shippingservice-0`, `shippingservice-1`, `shippingservice-2`\n   - **原因**: `client_error_ratio` 和 `error_ratio` 增加。\n   - **证据**: `error_ratio` 称最高达到 66.07 的值。\n\n### 综合分析\n这些异常指标表示服务之间的呼叫链在故障期间出现了显著的错误率增长和响应时间波动，尤其是 `frontend`, `checkoutservice`, `recommendationservice` 和 `shippingservice`。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\n    \"error_ratio\", \n    \"client_error_ratio\", \n    \"rrt\", \n    \"rrt_max\", \n    \"server_error_ratio\", \n    \"pod_cpu_usage\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max 显著增长，可能导致响应时间延迟。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max 225266.5 to 60001668.0\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio 和 client_error_ratio 增加，提示请求失败。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"error_ratio 从 0.0 增长到 14.81\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"recommendationservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max 显著增长，导致服务响应时间延迟。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max 正常 11790.5 模式 328421565.46\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"client_error_ratio 和 error_ratio 增加，导致服务请求失败。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"client_error_ratio 从 0.0 增长到 66.07\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```", "trace_analysis_findings": "通过对UUID为37de08d4-269的故障的跟踪数据进行分析，我发现了以下异常调用链和其相关的信息：\n\n### 关键发现\n\n1. **显著延迟**\n   - **Recommendation Service** 调用增多，主要在以下调用上：\n     - `frontend-0` 调用 `RecommendationService` 中的 `ListRecommendations` 方法，延迟倍数增加显著（~440倍）。异常期间的平均耗时为54761.368 ms，对比正常的124.078 ms。\n   \n2. **其他延迟增加调用**\n   - `frontend-2` 调用内部 `ProductCatalogService/GetProduct` ，延迟倍数增加显著，但在Recommendation服务库存在更高异常的情况下，可能受其影响。\n\n3. **高错误率**\n   - 错误状态码 `1 context canceled` 的比例较高（Recommendation service 的调用也普遍报告`context canceled`，表明这些可能是因过时或无法完成的请求导致，被视为正常处理的上下文取消）。\n\n### 详细数据分析\n\n- **RecommendationService异常延迟**：\n  - `frontend-0` 对 `RecommendationService/ListRecommendations` 调用：延迟从正常的 124.078 ms 增加到异常期间的 54761.368 ms。\n  - 与此类似的调用均出现在 `frontend-1` 和 `frontend-2` 到 `RecommendationService` 的调用中。\n\n- **ProductCatalogService次级延迟**：\n  - 对 `ProductCatalogService/GetProduct` 的调用延迟增加但没有上述延迟倍数严重，一些调用如 `frontend-0` 到 `ProductCatalogService-0`约 1.4 倍。\n\n### 结论\n\n根因可能在于 `RecommendationService` 的性能问题，导致请求极大延迟，并对其他服务延迟造成传递效应。`context canceled` 错误提示大量因延迟或超时引起的请求失败，而这些可能与 `RecommendationService` 故障引发的性能瓶颈有关。\n\n### JSON 输出格式\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\"rrt_max\", \"frontend->recommendationservice\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"RecommendationService\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"调用 frontend->recommendationservice 的延迟增加至正常时段的 440 倍\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n该异常主要指向 `RecommendationService` 的性能故障，影响系统整体响应时间。"}
